description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Chukcha purrs with a rating of 80, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 80, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 3 for East, 8 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30801-63891-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [80 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
